<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1336 gunēṁṭi caItra
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śuddha 8 mi guruvārānanu vāraṇasikaṭakāna
<lb n="3"/>jāḍēsvara śrīcaṁdanamahapātraṁḍu Itani tamu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁḍu pātrabadrēsvarajīyanaṁ I Idaṟunnu tamaku Abhī
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṣṭartasidhigānu śrīnarasiṁhyanātuniki nityamu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nnu Ubhayadhūpālanu satanu doṁḍāvanamālalu
<lb n="7"/>reṁḍu samarpriṁciri ṟēpaṁṭi dupana doṁḍa 1 rātri du
<lb n="8" break="no"/>pana doṁḍa 1 puUlādoṁḍalu Ireḍaṁ doṁḍalu tecipeṭa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nu bisaḷigaṁgu doṁḍa 1 phaḷu Anama Anavala tamuḍu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nu doṁḍa 1 I reḍu doṁḍalunnu peṭanu vīriki kuṭikiga
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṭu saItamugānu maḍalu 20 peṭiri Ivi Ācaṁdra
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rkastahigānu teci peṭaṁgalaru I darmmu śrīvaiṣṇava ra
<lb n="13" break="no"/>kṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

